highlights.text: Dangrangto has the most spots on Top Songs Vietnam. “Wrong Times” is the highest at #8.
“Lạ Lùng” by Vũ. has been on Top Songs Vietnam the longest, at 388 weeks straight.
“Không Buông” by Hngle and Ari is the highest new entry on Top Songs Vietnam at #51.
“APT.” by ROSÉ and Bruno Mars is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Vietnam, up 85 spots at #68.
